[[File:ScapioInRecopia.jpg|thumb|right|200px|The island-chain city of Scapio on Recopia]]
A chain of islands linked together by a series of bridges, '''Scapio''' was the capital of the planet [[Recopia]]&mdash;or at least, the closest the planet had to a capital.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

This settlement, where most offworlders gathered, was also home to [[Thoren Spaceport]], the only port on Recopia which serviced passenger starliners.<ref name="CCW" />

